{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"version","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/version","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>version</code></strong>&nbsp;属性用于指明&nbsp;SVG 文档遵循规范。&nbsp;它只允许在根元素<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\">&lt;svg&gt;</a>&nbsp;上使用。&nbsp;它纯粹是一个说明，对渲染或处理没有任何影响。</p>\n\n<p>虽然它接受任何数字，但是只有<code>1.0</code>&nbsp;和&nbsp;<code>1.1</code>.这两个有效的选择。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"usage_context","title":"Usage context","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>None</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#number\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/SVG/Content_type#Number\">&lt;number&gt;</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">动画属性</th>\n   <td>No</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">标准文件</th>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/struct.html#SVGElementVersionAttribute\" rel=\"external noopener\" class=\"external\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): version attribute</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Usage context","id":"usage_context"}],"summary":"version 属性用于指明 SVG 文档遵循规范。 它只允许在根元素<svg> 上使用。 它纯粹是一个说明，对渲染或处理没有任何影响。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"version","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"version","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"version","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/version","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/version/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发